Bitcoin Exchange Rate Program
-----------------------------

Using the CURL library ( https://curl.haxx.se/ ) for network request of the following
bitcoin exchange rate: https://blockchain.info/ticker

The information is presented in JSON format.

Use of the nlohmann JSON library (https://github.com/nlohmann/json) is necessary to
handle json data format.

The program will eventually print the current exchange rate:
1 BTC = 
        (AUD)     13461 $
        (BRL)     48247 R$
        (CAD)     12315 $
        (CHF)      8555 CHF
        (CLP)   7076139 $
        (CNY)     62882 ¥
        (DKK)     60299 kr
        (EUR)      8103 €
        (GBP)      7226 £
        (HKD)     68324 $
        (INR)    668162 ₹
        (ISK)   1249316 kr
        (JPY)    950474 ¥
        (KRW)  10938410 ₩
        (NZD)     14442 $
        (PLN)     36414 zł
        (RUB)    630772 RUB
        (SEK)     85260 kr
        (SGD)     12549 $
        (THB)    281600 ฿
        (TRY)     60045 ₺
        (TWD)    264886 NT$
        (USD)      8811 $
=============================================
INFORMATION:
  1. Developed in Linux Ubundu 20.04
  2. Developed in Visual Studio Code
  3. Download library for JSON handling from: https://github.com/nlohmann/json/tree/develop/single_include/nlohmann
  4. Download libcurl-dev package for your OS from here: https://curl.haxx.se/
  5. Compile command used: g++ --std=c++17 bitcoin.cpp -o bitcoin -lcurl
